"{\"uid\": \"somersetcountygazette.co.uk-news-somerset_news-24491097.becky-wilde-represents-somerset-achieving-olympic-podium\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"2024 Paris Olympic GamesRowingSportSomerset  A ROWER from Somerset has won a bronze medal in this year's Olympics\\u00a0in Paris after beating out some big nations including at 'death' qualifiers earlier this year.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somerset\", \"score\": 0.9999123347240408, \"rank\": 8.767296181347859e-05, \"text\": \"Somerset\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somerset\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somerset\"}, {\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994543374339, \"rank\": 5.456630622163967e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Becky Wilde, 26,\\u00a0was born in Trull and competed in the women's double scull this year with rowing partner Mathilda Hodgkins Byrne, 29.\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999466333836226, \"rank\": 5.2864035770437184e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trull\", \"score\": 0.9999940233711981, \"rank\": 5.976664541529227e-06, \"text\": \"Trull\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trull\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trull\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matilda_australia\", \"score\": 0.7908240701537502, \"rank\": 0.1989304812833776, \"text\": \"Mathilda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matilda_australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matilda_australia\"}, {\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkins,_Illinois\", \"score\": 0.9806335237791598, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hodgkins\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkins,_Illinois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkins,_Illinois\"}, {\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Byrne\", \"score\": 0.9999853105028962, \"rank\": 1.46897044336356e-05, \"text\": \"Byrne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Byrne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Holding the silver medal position for most of the race, the duo representing Team GBfell just short of second to Romaniabut did well to beat out the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.8795444124831409, \"rank\": 0.10773154565548533, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the race, Wilde said:\\u00a0\\\"I had the support of so many great people behind me.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999466333836226, \"rank\": 5.2864035770437184e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have learnt so much and I know if I do my job, she (Mathilda) will get me over the line.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matilda_australia\", \"score\": 0.7908240701537502, \"rank\": 0.1989304812833776, \"text\": \"Mathilda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matilda_australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matilda_australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It will take a long time to sink in, it was amazing.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is so many years of hard work as I have always dreamed of coming here to the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was only her third international tournament and her debut Olympics.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The racing partners had to overcome a lot of challenges to reach Paris\\u00a0with both\\u00a0rowers labelling their appearance at this year's Olympics as \\\"a bit of a shock.\\\"\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994543374339, \"rank\": 5.456630622163967e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DOUBLE-TROUBLE!\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd1d \\ud83e\\udd49pic.twitter.com/oKYaFe32ei  Wilde and Hodgkins Byrne\\u00a0had toqualify for the Olympics through a series of gruelling qualifiersin May where they competed in\\u00a0Lucerne, Switzerland.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkins,_Illinois\", \"score\": 0.9806335237791598, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hodgkins\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkins,_Illinois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkins,_Illinois\"}, {\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Byrne\", \"score\": 0.9999853105028962, \"rank\": 1.46897044336356e-05, \"text\": \"Byrne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucerne\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 5.163300861670548e-12, \"text\": \"Lucerne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucerne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucerne\"}, {\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9928677397982781, \"rank\": 0.0071818806265836425, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The qualifiers in Switzerland are known as the 'Regatta of Death'.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9928677397982781, \"rank\": 0.0071818806265836425, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde was born in Trull but has a Welsh mother.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trull\", \"score\": 0.9999940233711981, \"rank\": 5.976664541529227e-06, \"text\": \"Trull\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trull\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trull\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.9635229418988572, \"rank\": 0.026809631581881606, \"text\": \"Welsh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a decade in the water swimming for Wales, she switched to rowing.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.9376339785383749, \"rank\": 0.04330384869214015, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finishing third was by no means easy, as both Wilde and Hodgkins Byrne faced some huge challenges in qualifying and outside of qualifying.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999466333836226, \"rank\": 5.2864035770437184e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde's Olympic preparations were set back last year as she picked up an injury.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999466333836226, \"rank\": 5.2864035770437184e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had surgery for 'compartment syndrome' in both her arms, a condition which causes pressure to build inside the muscles.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Luckily, she battled back to compete in Paris with her Hodgkins-Byrne, who\\u00a0competed in the last Olympics in Tokyo but then\\u00a0decided it was time for a break.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994543374339, \"rank\": 5.456630622163967e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999805160417778, \"rank\": 0.00019130485386377195, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympian is now a mother of two-year-old son Freddie, who was watching her from the grandstand.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998671751288, \"rank\": 1.3282467458515538e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde\\u00a0went to Queen's College in Taunton and was successful in competing at a high level in swimming during her time there, just before she took up rowing.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taunton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.798175129057919e-15, \"text\": \"Taunton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taunton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taunton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a social media post, Queen's College said: \\\"We are bursting with pride here at Queen's College Taunton.\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taunton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.798175129057919e-15, \"text\": \"Taunton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taunton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taunton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your hard work, talent, and determination have paid off in such a remarkable way.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have shown us all what it means to aim high and achieve great things!\\\"\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's     Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a complaint about the editorial content which relates to     inaccuracy or intrusion, then pleasecontact the editor here.\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are dissatisfied with the response provided you cancontact IPSO here  \\u00a9 2001-2025.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Somerset County Gazetteis owned and operated by Newsquest Media Group Ltd, an audited local newspaper network.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newsquest Media Group Ltd\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitnewsquest.co.ukto view ourpoliciesandterms.\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Echo Building, 18 Albert Road, Bournemouth, England BH1 1BZ.\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3002, \"end\": 3010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Daily_Echo\", \"score\": 0.9997530757891506, \"rank\": 0.0002469851973975568, \"text\": \"The Echo\", \"types\": [\"Q386